      section#about
        .content
          img.logo src="img/aboutlogo.png" 
          p Tinybright, as the name implies, consists of a tiny but bright group of 3 talented people from the city of Adelaide in Australia. Their collective dedication to making games that not only entertain, but educate along the way is the driving force behind Tinybright.
          span.info
            img src="img/about_amy.png"
            p Amy literally brings Tinybright to life. It’s her seemingly endless imagination, illustrations and animation skills that create the wonderful characters that bring so much joy to our work. Despite her talent, Amy still can’t believe she gets paid to do what she absolutely loves doing.
          span.info
            img src="img/about_lachlan.png"
            p Lachlan, in a word, is a genius. His versatility and extensive knowledge in an array of programming languages helps turn Tinybright’s vision into a reality. His years of experience are fundamental in delivering a product that is seamless and marketable.
          span.info
            img src="img/about_becq.png"
            p Becq is an acclaimed, award winning art director. Her vast experience in the advertising industry equips her with invaluable wisdom, from concept development and interface design, through to music and sound production. Becq is the master coordinator. Without her, Tinybright wouldn’t shine as bright.
          p Together, our aim is to create high quality and memorable products with an unrivalled attention to detail. We hope you love them as much as we have loved making them.
